The dataset is fully synthetic. No real person, organisation, or
incident is referenced. Differential privacy parameter epsilon = 0.8
has been applied to numeric fields. All scenarios are aligned with
the Turkish SHGM SHT-SIBER Annex 13 standard incident analysis
format.
